Anda menjaga semua orang.

00:20:07.040 --> 00:20:08.320
Kaashvi!

00:20:08.760 --> 00:20:09.960
Kemarilah.

00:20:12.600 --> 00:20:14.040
Duduk.  Hati-hati.

